Material used in the molecular genetic analysis. HU1608314; China : Hebei prov.: Tang River (1). (GenBank accession number: KY451917 ).—HU1600026; China : Hebei prov.: Xiaoluan River, upper Luan River drainage, 41°69′N 117°01′E (2). (GenBank accession number: KY451914 ).—HU1608311; China : Hebei prov.: Shandian River, upper Luan River drainage, 41°68′N 115°79′E (3). (GenBank accession number: KY451919 ).— HU1608040; China : Liaoning prov.: Nu’er River, upper Xiaoling River drainage, 40°84′N 120°36′E (9). (GenBank accession number:
